name: Robotdono: Teknologi Perrobotan
description:
Robotic technology X Indonesian local wisdom? It's the robot that appears in Warkop DKI Sama Juga Bohong Movie (1986). It's really absurd, a robot that sells bajigur. What's a bajigur? You can google it.

Search "Warkop DKI Sama Juga Bohong" on Youtube for context.
